address2: Floors 15, 16, and 17 Opposite of City Center P.O.Box 16875
longBusinessSummary: Qatar Industrial Manufacturing Company Q.P.S.C., together with its subsidiaries, engages in industrial manufacturing and various types of industrial investments in Qatar and internationally. The company produces treated sand for construction and agricultural uses; paving stones and kerb stones; sulphuric acid for local and export markets; and non-colored and colored aluminum profiles, as well as converts facial tissues, toilet rolls, kitchen rolls, and M Tork rolls. It serves chemicals, petrochemicals, construction materials, and food processing industries. The company was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Doha, Qatar.
